\begin{document}
$$\lbrack Ca \rbrack_{in} = b \times Kd(R - R_{min})/(R_{max} - R)$$
\end{document}. Calibration constants were determined in separate experiments with the same experimental set-up, as described previously (Sorimachi et al. [27]).
